This directory contains a template for creating a CodeIgniter-based
application. The directories here come from within the CodeIgniter
distribution, under the "application" directory.

The index.php file is this template has the correct settings for
system and application folder. The system folder is path to the
CodeIgniter system directory, which will be
/usr/local/share/htdocs/codeigniter_1.6.3/system

The application folder is set to the directory of this application,
that is, ".".
